Target: OntoAssetManagement is an ontology that extends P2P-O, a purchase-to-pay ontology and it is designed to represent asset, purchase and organizations information.

Comment: A legal document that authorizes the transportation of goods from one location to another.

Comment: Inventory identifier assigned to an item.
